name: mikroe.click.gnss11
short_description: GNSS 11 Click is a compact add-on board that provides fast positioning capability. This board features the EVA-M8M, a concurrent GNSS module from u-blox. The module provides a reception of GPS, GLONASS, Galileo, QZSS, SBAS, and BeiDou. It delivers high sensitivity and minimal acquisition times, with concurrent reception of up to three GNSS, achieved by a dual-frequency RF front-end architecture. This Click boardâ„¢ makes the perfect solution for the development of both acquisition and tracking devices and represents an ideal product for automotive, consumer, and industrial tracking applications.
